author: jsdelfino
msg: Initialize service binding URI to componentURI/bindingName if no URI is specified on a binding. Binding extensions do not need to implement the logic to determine the default binding URI anymore (except for any binding specific logic, including use of a specific protocol scheme), they can simply call binding.getURI() to get that URI. Also cleaned up up SCABinding as SCABinding.get/setComponent are not needed anymore.
